2. FDUSD has completed the first redemption and maintained 1:1 full support;
3. Justin Sun will respond to the First Digital Trust incident in a few hours;
4. The founder of Mask Network responded to the abnormal drop in MASK price: the solution will be announced within 1-2 days;
5. First Digital Labs destroyed 87 million FDUSD in the past 24 hours;
6. The giant whale released the pledge and recharged 71,448 SOL to Binance, worth 8.54 million US dollars;
7. Justin Sun: "I am Ultraman", Techteryx is not an industry under his name, if TUSD cannot be cashed or trigger a financial storm;
8. Russia may allow the conversion of seized BTC into national fiscal revenue;
9. Superseed launched Genesis Passport, a limited edition commemorative mainnet launch;
10. Treasure The game and Treasure Chain operations will be terminated due to financial crisis;
11. The crypto market sector fell across the board, BTC fell below $84,000, and only the RWA sector remained relatively strong.
